An instand classic with neck-thru construction, EMG pickups and locking tuners. The ESP LTD Will Adler Warbird Electric Guitar is an affordable way to lift your playing to new heights. It offers a familiar and comfortably contoured mahogany body with neck-thru construction. The ultrafast neck has an extra-thin U profile, ebony fingerboard and 22 extra-jumbo frets. Seymour Duncan humbucking pickups put out plenty of volume and are wired to individual Volume controls, a 3-way toggle and a Master Tone for expanded sound shaping. Black hardware is used throughout including the LTD locking tuners and tune-o-matic bridge.
